{"categories":["service-promotion","seasonal","media-entertainment","activism","global-observances-celebrations"],"collections":"","description":"Celebrate Women's Equality Day with our exclusive podcast template, designed to amplify gender rights discussions and inspire action. Perfect for media, entertainment, and activism platforms, this audio template provides a compelling way to honor global observances and celebrations. Promote your service while engaging your audience in meaningful conversations about women's equality. This podcast template is not just about seasonal promotions, it's about fostering a deeper understanding and appreciation for women's rights. Engage your audience, promote awareness, and elevate your brand with our Women's Equality Day podcast template. Stand for equality, empower your listeners, and make every day a Women's Equality Day.","short_description":"Promote Women's Equality Day with our dedicated podcast template. Ideal for media, entertainment, and activism platforms, it fosters discussions on gender rights and global celebrations. Engage your audience in meaningful dialogue and elevate your brand. Stand for equality, empower your listeners today.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/IMG_20220307_130329.jpg","description":"I am a web and graphic designer deeply fascinated by UI/UX. Constantly upgrading my skills, I strive to create visually stunning and user-friendly designs and digital experiences that leave a lasting impact.","short_description":"","display_name":"Nore Potera","id":"nore-potera"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings><o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch><o:AllowPNG/></o:Off